The paper deals with information fusion in neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper specifically focuses on deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning that deals with neural networks. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with computer vision (cs.CV) and neural engineering (cs.NE), which are related to the application of deep learning in image processing and biological systems, respectively. Finally, the paper discusses optimization techniques for neural networks, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
